Credentialing

Virtual Assistants

Can you startup with zero staff? We take on frontdesk responsibility until you are ready to hire a full time employee.

Coding & Authorizations

Lack of coding knowledge will result in significantly higher denials with procedures and surgeries. Getting prior authorization for surgeries and procedures can take hours of your staff’s time. We take care of coding your surgeries and get prior authorizations for your tests.
